cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY. 

The paper proposes a deep reinforcement learning solution to the grasping problem using 2.5D images as the only source of information. The paper involves robotics (cs.RO) and computer vision (cs.CV) as it uses depth camera images to guide the robot's grasping task. The paper also involves machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) as it uses deep reinforcement learning algorithms to learn how to solve the grasping task. Finally, the paper involves control systems (cs.SY) as it aims to control the robot's actions to achieve the grasping task.
